33:08.560 --> 33:09.400
That's today.

33:10.640 --> 33:13.280
-That's great, we'll go.
-We?

33:14.480 --> 33:16.000
Why should I take you with me?

33:16.400 --> 33:18.720
Because I know where HollÃ¤nder is
and you don't.

33:19.120 --> 33:20.600
And no one else you know does.

33:20.880 --> 33:23.760
-And if they knew they wouldn't tell you.
-Oh yeah?

33:24.120 --> 33:26.040
Yes, you're the police.

33:29.400 --> 33:30.240
Are you eating this?

33:39.840 --> 33:42.400
Ortgies, 6.35 calibre.
What does that tell you?

33:43.720 --> 33:45.600
-Would be fitting for Kardakov.
-Why?

33:46.280 --> 33:47.480
It's a "weapon for the opera".

33:48.120 --> 33:50.240
Used by people
who don't know how to shoot.

33:50.600 --> 33:52.800
Musicians, artists, and such like.

33:57.080 --> 33:59.520
So, tonight, 9 p.m. at HollÃ¤nder.

34:00.800 --> 34:05.120
Nine? No point in going there
before midnight. More like 1 or 2 a.m.

34:07.240 --> 34:10.840
-Alright, midnight then.
-Friedrichstrasse station. It's nearby.

34:13.720 --> 34:17.480
I'm with <i>WeltbÃ¼hne.</i>
I'm an accredited journalist. Excuse me...

34:22.560 --> 34:23.600
Hello, neighbor.

34:24.240 --> 34:26.880
Mr. Katelbach. What's going on?

34:26.960 --> 34:29.560
Your <i>Presidentsky</i>
is trying to save his honor.

34:29.640 --> 34:32.160
Like, if the reds shoot, so can we.

34:32.240 --> 34:35.960
I'm afraid we're missing half of it.
You wouldn't happen to know a back door?

34:36.040 --> 34:37.840
<i>Gentlemen,</i>
<i>welcome to this press conference.</i>

34:39.480 --> 34:43.200
<i>We called it to shed the right light</i>
<i>on some things.</i>

34:43.280 --> 34:44.800
-Excuse me.
-Excuse me.

34:45.320 --> 34:47.880
Excuse me. The gentleman is with me.

34:48.840 --> 34:51.880
It wasn't the police
who incited the riots,

34:52.000 --> 34:54.160
but the communist associations

34:54.240 --> 34:58.120
who, without any respect of state order,

34:58.200 --> 35:02.000
called for an attack on the police forces

35:02.080 --> 35:06.840
who were there for de-escalation.

35:08.120 --> 35:11.320
Let me introduce one of our heroes to you,

35:11.640 --> 35:14.280
whose brave commitment for law and order

35:14.360 --> 35:17.800
received a hail of bullets from
trigger-happy Bolsheviks in thanks.

35:18.080 --> 35:19.920
Constable Fritz DÃ¶rr.

35:24.640 --> 35:25.800
A true hero, him?

35:27.640 --> 35:28.560
Lies!

35:29.080 --> 35:30.040
<i>Boom.</i>

35:32.000 --> 35:32.880
Great.

35:33.160 --> 35:34.880
On behalf of the Fatherland: Thank you.

35:35.320 --> 35:36.200
Great.

