42:36.080 --> 42:37.280
-And you?
-Me?

42:37.600 --> 42:40.120
Go steady? Spare me.

42:40.840 --> 42:43.160
Why do people see that differently,
but not in Berlin?

42:43.240 --> 42:46.520
We're just a bit faster than the rest.
Of the fair people.

42:46.600 --> 42:48.600
Always a quick answer,
even if it isn't one.

42:48.880 --> 42:50.640
A quick answer is better
than slow silence right?

42:50.920 --> 42:52.080
And always the last word. No.

43:42.040 --> 43:43.160
What time is it? I'll take you home now.

43:47.840 --> 43:48.760
No.

43:48.840 --> 43:50.000
But I have to run.

43:50.080 --> 43:51.280
No back talk.

43:52.480 --> 43:54.320
This is most kind, Mr. Rath, but...

43:54.840 --> 43:56.080
I have plans.

43:57.600 --> 43:58.560
See you tomorrow.

44:02.960 --> 44:03.800
Home after all?

44:09.680 --> 44:10.680
No, but...

44:11.640 --> 44:13.800
do I get paid by someone for this?

44:16.600 --> 44:18.240
For my work?

44:20.800 --> 44:22.000
I have no idea.

44:23.880 --> 44:24.800
How do you mean?

44:27.840 --> 44:29.280
We've only just started.

44:30.640 --> 44:32.520
Alright. Bye.

45:31.840 --> 45:35.040
<i>It must be just a dream</i>

45:35.480 --> 45:40.000
<i>Trying to snatch the wind</i>

45:40.080 --> 45:43.720
<i>Who really knows?</i>

45:46.520 --> 45:49.640
<i>The clock on your wall</i>

45:50.120 --> 45:53.280
<i>It is filled with sand</i>

45:53.840 --> 45:57.520
<i>Put your hand in mine</i>

45:57.600 --> 46:00.360
<i>And let us be forever</i>

46:01.280 --> 46:04.520
<i>Now you make your choice</i>

46:04.880 --> 46:09.440
<i>And throw us</i>
<i>in between happiness and agony</i>

46:09.520 --> 46:13.880
<i>But I can forgive you</i>

46:15.880 --> 46:18.960
<i>You are very close to death</i>

46:19.480 --> 46:22.520
<i>But your eye still clear</i>

46:22.600 --> 46:25.880
<i>Does it recognize me? I'm ready</i>

46:25.960 --> 46:31.320
<i>To seek immortality with you</i>
